Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.08,0:03:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}风学姐 姿势自然点就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.32,0:03:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只是下意识啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.02,0:03:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}话说你最近很热衷摄影啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.00,0:03:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}学姐快要毕业了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.70,0:03:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}留下社员们的活动纪录是很重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.91,0:03:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不过我就算毕业 也会常来这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.68,0:03:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}还要待在这里啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.36,0:03:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我就猜到你会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.87,0:03:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嘴上这么说其实很高兴吧 夏凛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.73,0:03:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你这是什么反应
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.17,0:03:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看着她们就涌起我的创作欲啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.44,0:03:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你也觉得吧 桑乔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.62,0:03:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.88,0:03:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这孩子能说话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.20,0:03:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}风风学姐和小鱼干给我好多灵感
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.77,0:03:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我回去就以她们为原型写本书
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.01,0:03:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.89,0:03:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}再见
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.42,0:03:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.31,0:03:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}再见 园园
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.62,0:03:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}给我等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.98,0:04:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}对了 毕业旅行去哪里好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.17,0:04:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}年末的时候哪里都没去成
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.86,0:04:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就是啊 用大赦的公费一起去泡温泉怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.39,0:04:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我之前去泡过温泉 能换个地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.03,0:04:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}登山也很不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.81,0:04:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}登山？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.04,0:04:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}迷路的小猫咪 你在哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.23,0:04:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}找不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.60,0:04:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}对了树 用猫语叫它出来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.02,0:04:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喵～喵～喵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.30,0:04:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}再…再野性一点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.06,0:04:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真棒 寸寸真棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.16,0:04:40.84,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.84,0:04:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}请不要拍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.90,0:04:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.71,0:04:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}过来 一起回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.13,0:04:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}乖乖
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.67,0:04:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈好眼力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.84,0:04:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我吓到它了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.97,0:05:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}寻找小猫的委托完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.27,0:05:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}学姐 拍一张照留作纪念吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.41,0:05:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.41,0:05:14.64,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}その先でまた会えるから
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.41,0:05:14.64,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}在漫长旅路的前方与你重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.64,0:05:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你们唱得真好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.57,0:05:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}配合也完美
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.84,0:05:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们也来唱一首吧 友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.50,0:05:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 等一下就写作业
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.28,0:05:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}睡糊涂了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.16,0:05:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小鱼干 我们一起唱个痛快吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.10,0:05:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.78,0:05:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.97,0:05:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}夏凛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.80,0:05:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}能聊一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.90,0:05:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}聊什么 夏凛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.97,0:05:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}去走走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.40,0:05:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好久没来这边了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.23,0:06:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}上次救东乡的时候来过而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.44,0:06:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.88,0:06:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我能先问个问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.37,0:06:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}夏凛不冷吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.28,0:06:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱歉 我都没考虑到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.26,0:06:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}换个地方吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.58,0:06:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不要紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.15,0:06:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这样就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.07,0:06:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.19,0:06:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}之前风说过 毕业后也会常来社团吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.27,0:06:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.65,0:06:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我听她那么说或许有点开心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.10,0:06:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有点？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.32,0:06:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就一点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.20,0:06:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是…也还是很…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.99,0:06:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}很高兴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.08,0:06:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.39,0:07:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你看 我也学会把心里话说出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.04,0:07:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈也说出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.51,0:07:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}年末这阵子 友奈你好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.92,0:07:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一定发生什么了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.88,0:07:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我会帮助你的 能告诉我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.63,0:07:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.55,0:07:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}没什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.51,0:07:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.47,0:07:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不管是什么烦恼 我都能接受
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.38,0:07:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我很在乎你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.68,0:07:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}夏凛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.07,0:07:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我会帮你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.73,0:07:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只要是为了你 我什么都愿意做
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.24,0:07:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我好高兴 有个朋友能让我这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.45,0:07:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是友奈你们 让我有这份心的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.16,0:07:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}夏凛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.20,0:07:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}发生什么事了 友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.80,0:08:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.44,0:08:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真的…没什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.32,0:08:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.94,0:08:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}夏凛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.69,0:08:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}勇者社不是…「有烦恼要跟大家说」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.69,0:08:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我真的很想帮上朋友的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.17,0:08:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}夏凛 等一下 夏凛！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.94,0:08:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}对不起 对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.28,0:09:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈最近的样子果然不太对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.44,0:09:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是大吉耶 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.20,0:09:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不对 抽到大吉的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.98,0:09:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈会笑得更灿烂才对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.41,0:09:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但为何她的表情看上去这么难受
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.64,0:09:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她肯定碰上什么不好跟我们说的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.45,0:09:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.73,0:09:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我来查明真相
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.50,0:09:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康黑体W7\bord0.2\blur5\shad3\3c&H304133&\4c&H35724F&\pos(320,605)}目标
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.25,0:09:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康黑体W7\bord0.2\blur5\shad3\3c&H304133&\4c&H35724F&\pos(475,605)}睡眠中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.04,0:09:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康黑体W7\bord0.2\blur5\shad3\3c&H304133&\4c&H35724F&\pos(730,605)}可以入侵室内。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.71,0:09:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康黑体W7\bord0.2\blur5\shad3\3c&H120F07&\4c&H120F07&\pos(430,605)}收到。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.46,0:09:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康黑体W7\bord0.2\blur5\shad3\3c&H120F07&\4c&H120F07&\pos(625,605)}请原地待命。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.18,0:09:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康黑体W7\bord0.2\blur5\shad3\3c&H304133&\4c&H35724F&\pos(400,605)}开始入侵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.30,0:09:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康黑体W7\bord0.2\blur5\shad3\3c&H304133&\4c&H35724F&\pos(700,605)}请打开锁。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.68,0:09:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康黑体W7\bord0.2\blur5\shad3\3c&H304133&\4c&H35724F&\pos(530,605)}收到。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.75,0:10:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈 灯都没关就睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.65,0:10:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱歉 我偷偷进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.44,0:10:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有线索吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.03,0:10:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那是！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.79,0:10:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈刚上中学时 4月3日托父母买却从未翻过的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.39,0:10:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这套丛书居然有一本凸了出来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.99,0:10:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}勇者御记…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.03,0:10:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}为什么里面藏着这个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.00,0:10:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可能…不对 这里面肯定有线索
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.74,0:10:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.80,0:11:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.15,0:11:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我就借走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.58,0:11:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这是友奈写的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.26,0:11:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈最近的样子很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.24,0:11:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}原因可能就写在这里面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.25,0:11:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}居然还有这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.64,0:11:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我能插句话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.67,0:11:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}园园？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.35,0:11:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也担心悠悠 就调查了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.33,0:11:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我最近不是比大家早回去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.61,0:11:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}其实是去大赦的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.16,0:11:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大赦…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.73,0:11:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我先说结论 悠悠的样子会不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.52,0:11:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}其实是因为受天神的神罚所苦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.80,0:11:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}园园 你是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.22,0:11:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}听我说 鹫鹫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.18,0:11:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}根据大赦的调查
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.73,0:12:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果悠悠把神罚说出来 写下来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.14,0:12:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}神罚便会传染
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.75,0:12:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以这本日记是非常危险的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.64,0:12:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你们还是要看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.92,0:12:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}当然 我很担心友奈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.82,0:12:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那一起来看悠悠的御记吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.92,0:12:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}最开始是在年末
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.12,0:12:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大赦的人发觉我情况有异 专程上门来找我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.12,0:12:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他们通过神嘱和研究 已经查明了情况
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.45,0:12:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他们希望我能写日记 留下神圣的记录
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.05,0:12:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}便给了我这本御记
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.68,0:12:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我能坚持下去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.93,0:12:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}为什么会变这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.03,0:13:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我在大战中受到了巨大的消耗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.37,0:13:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}全身几乎散花殆尽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.25,0:13:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我甚至因为触碰到了敌人的御魂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.24,0:13:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}自己的灵魂也被御魂吸走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.15,0:13:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等我醒过来 那里是我救东乡的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.01,0:13:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是一片辽阔无垠的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.17,0:13:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我奋力挣扎 想要逃出这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.70,0:13:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这里却是那么的宽广 走也走不出去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.09,0:13:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家 救救我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.47,0:13:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就算孤身一人 勇者也…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.48,0:14:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}勇者也不会放弃战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.84,0:14:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}东乡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.97,0:14:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只要信念还在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.51,0:14:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}东乡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.36,0:14:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}希望就不会消散…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.35,0:14:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}东乡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.05,0:14:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}无论有任何代价 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.83,0:14:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}东乡 东乡 东乡！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.61,0:14:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我 不希望 失去最宝贵的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.65,0:14:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}东乡在哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.91,0:14:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我 我 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.04,0:14:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.28,0:14:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}勇者不会对哭泣的朋友坐视不理
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.13,0:14:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}勇者就看毅力 我一定要回去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.95,0:15:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}蓝乌鸦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.46,0:15:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我想蓝乌鸦是叫我跟它走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.24,0:15:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以我朝着光芒的方向不断前行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.69,0:15:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}于是我终于回到了这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.99,0:15:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但身体却不一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.99,0:15:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我和大家从散花状态恢复了过来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.16,0:15:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但并非是献上的祭品回到了我们身上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.67,0:15:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}恢复的身体能力是神树大人创造的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.62,0:16:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}花了很多时间 才成了我们自己身体的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.82,0:16:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}为了治愈强行盛开 最后散花的我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.95,0:16:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}神树大人把我全身都变成了自己做的零件
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.90,0:16:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大赦称我为「御姿」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.47,0:16:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}「御姿」说好听点 是种非常神圣的存在
